            <p><choice corresp="#a1 #a2 #a3 #a4 #b1 #b2 #b3 #b4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:ogihara2009"/><citedRange>200-201</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:couvreur1959"/><citedRange>251</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>397f</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:couvreur1959"/><citedRange>251</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">Behält er [es, scil. das zusätzliche Gewand] darüber hinaus, [so ist] das Gewand abzugeben.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">[If] he keeps [it, i.e. the extra garment] beyond that, the garment [must be] ceded.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>397-8</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>303</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:couvreur1959"/><citedRange>251</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:couvreur1959"/><citedRange>251</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">[when] the garment of a monk is finished [and] the kaṭhina-time has passed</seg></seg></choice></p>
         </div>
